| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5828 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf1ffbab-d387-5604-ac1f-552a0e889b7d"
